#Approach:
Left Rotate Array by One – Approach (Hinglish)

1. Sabse pehle first element ko ek temporary variable me store kar lo (kyunki woh overwrite ho jayega).
2. Phir array ko left shift karo:
    i = 1 se n-1 tak loop chalao
    Har element ko ek position left shift kar do
    nums[i-1] = nums[i]
3. Ab last index pe temporary wala first element daal do.
4. Array left rotate ho jayega by 1.

#Code:
class Solution {
    public void rotateArrayByOne(int[] nums) {
        int temp = nums[0];
        int n = nums.length;
        for(int i=1; i<n; i++){
            nums[i-1] = nums[i];
        }
        nums[n-1] = temp;
    }
}
